http://www.offshore.com.ai/vince, who lives in Anguilla, a true
tropical paradise, and rents a nice home for $500 a month, and pays
zero income tax. (check out the view from his house at
www.offshore.com.ai/vince/view.jpg , that's St. Martin/Maarten in the
